  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Male participation in reducing early marriages</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will enhance male participation in the fight against early, forced marriages in the rural areas of Masaiti District of Zambia; by engaging and dialoguing with 310 men and boys, formation of Men/Boys Take Action (MBTA) groups; addressing negative factors that exacerbate child marriages including community acceptance of early marriages, tradition and cultural norms that undermine girl&apos;s abilities to make decisions on their reproductive, education and health rights in rural areas.</narrative>
  </description>
